          "en": "he was still the same good old self"
        },
        {
          "no": "av godt, gammelt merke",
          "en": "of good old make"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "text": "som har sitt opphav i fortiden",
      "translation": "which has its origin in the past",
      "examples": []
    },
    {
      "text": "som har vart lenge",
      "translation": "which has lasted a long time",
      "examples": [
        {
          "no": "vi er gamle venner",
          "en": "we are old friends"
        },
        {
          "no": "gammelt vennskap",
          "en": "old friendship"
        },
        {
          "no": "gammel gjeld",
          "en": "old debt"
        },
        {
          "no": "slå den gamle rekorden",
          "en": "beat the old record"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "text": "som har vært lenge i en bestemt rolle, et bestemt yrke eller lignende",
      "translation": "who has been in a certain role, a certain profession for a long time",
      "examples": [
        {
          "no": "en gammel jeger",
          "en": "an old hunter"
        },
        {
